<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-969CF1CE-3EBF-4ADB-B71A-B54BB4CA2BF4" version="1" lang="en-US"?><task xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-969CF1CE-3EBF-4ADB-B71A-B54BB4CA2BF4" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic task)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c task oceTask-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">Replace the rollers of the Xtran pinch</title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="GUID-C14193DA-344F-42C3-884A-E8764FE68AF1"><p class="- topic/p ">You can replace the Xtran pinch rollers without service assistance. The total amount of rollers over the full width of the printer is 32. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Video: <ph class="- topic/ph " varid="Video: 15 - Replace the rollers of the Xtran pinch"><xref class="- topic/xref " format="html" href="https://sus.cpp.canon/0YPQA00S" scope="external"><?ditaot usertext?> 
<image class="- topic/image " href="GUID-1B93C780-C233-4810-947C-7EC17F913975-low.png" placement="inline" otherprops="GUID-1B93C780-C233-4810-947C-7EC17F913975-low.png"/> Replace the rollers of the Xtran pinch</xref></ph>. 
</p><fig class="- topic/fig " id="GUID-FBF39D4B-E0D2-43B5-B17E-F56F22DF8030"><title class="- topic/title ">The clamp and the roller with axis</title><image class="- topic/image " href="GUID-F22F459F-35C9-48DB-9D39-2A93A2B803C1-low.png" placement="inline" otherprops="GUID-F22F459F-35C9-48DB-9D39-2A93A2B803C1-low.png"/></fig></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">User task</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><prereq id="PREREQ_EE24CF19BBE4443786BF413DF22F356D" class="- topic/section task/prereq "><p class="- topic/p ">Use <ph varid="productname" class="- topic/ph ">Colorado M-Series</ph> prescribed: 
</p><ul id="UL_1FD256E79DF940B8A41F66714B60E91B" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_0AAC9E2E843E4F0CA1E6ECFE3E027011" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> <ph translate="no" class="- topic/ph ">Microflex</ph> gloves for handling ink 
</p></li><li id="LI_706EE85B1EFF415A85FBE7F8FC04ED77" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Xtran pinch rollers, axis and clamps 
</p></li><li id="LI_A9492FCBD53A459CB87DBBC0D3B9F4AC" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Small screwdriver 
</p></li><li id="LI_3CF58D1D3C0B44BABE7AF75493867F88" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Piece of paper (A3) 
</p></li></ul><note id="GUID-62C33CBE-1F72-4A59-88D5-8F8E8A8EF188" class="- topic/note " type="caution"><p class="- topic/p "> Wear gloves when contact with ink or maintenance materials is possible. Gloves should always overlap sleeves. Wear safety glasses with side shields when handling ink or maintenance materials. Follow the ink related Safety Data Sheets (SDS) guidelines carefully in order to ensure maximum safety. 
</p></note></prereq><steps id="GUID-363DDAF2-D4EC-48C3-9F0D-994DD78900E6" class="- topic/ol task/steps "><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Move to the media input side and open the top cover. 
</cmd></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Put on the <ph varid="productname" class="- topic/ph ">Colorado M-Series</ph> approved gloves. 
</cmd></step><step id="d68602e73" class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Carefully push the printhead carriage to the left in manual maintenance position (1). 
</cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><note type="important" id="d68602e77" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Touch the printhead carriage on the covered area only, otherwise you can damage the printheads. 
</p></note></info><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><fig id="d68602e81" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-CF19DD7C-1A90-43E0-B7C4-1B8A93EA891C-low.png" id="d68602e82" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-CF19DD7C-1A90-43E0-B7C4-1B8A93EA891C-low.png"/></fig></info></step><step id="d68602e83" class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Take a piece of paper and place it under the Xtran roller you want to replace (2). 
</cmd></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd "> Remove the black clamp from the axis. 
</cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><p class="- topic/p ">Use the small screwdriver to push the black plastic part of the axis on both sides away from the unit. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Only push at the top of the plastic part otherwise you will break the axis holder. 
</p><fig id="d68602e94" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-8FAE1CD5-8564-4480-9C83-2DD6C61C0A0C-low.png" id="d68602e95" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-8FAE1CD5-8564-4480-9C83-2DD6C61C0A0C-low.png"/></fig></info></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Remove the axis from the holder. 
</cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><fig id="d68602e100" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-B1AB414B-2207-4076-80CE-6C2DE2E64163-low.png" id="d68602e101" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-B1AB414B-2207-4076-80CE-6C2DE2E64163-low.png"/></fig></info></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Remove the roller from the holder. 
</cmd></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Take the new roller and place it into the holder. 
</cmd></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Insert the new axis through the holder and the roller. 
</cmd></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Install the new black clamp onto the axis. 
</cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><p class="- topic/p ">To ease installing the black clamp, lift the roll upwards slightly.
</p></info></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Dispose the rollers, axis, clamps and gloves as chemical waste according to local regulations. 
</cmd></step></steps></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-99B79551-BE67-41AD-95FC-BDB28BED4A4E.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>User task</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
</task>